column2: Shake your hand in the air 8 times while counting to 8
Do it as fast and loud as you can
Repeat with your other hand and both feet
Do it 7 times, then 6 times until you get to 1.
Call out “Crazy chicken” as loud as you can!
Have you released all your stress? If not, do it again even faster and louder! ",,,,,,,,,,,,,,,a5a25ea4-9472-42b0-9d9f-a86b3d6970f1,,execute_actions,;
